## Non-goals

- Flipping ambient default off Vosk in this task (dogfood first)
- Full TUI for multi-engine (guided CLI + skill SETUP is enough)
- Replacing cloud STT for utterance body
- Training custom wake models in-process (see I006 enrollment samples)
- Re-implementing already-landed name/voice defaults

