## Enrollment samples (I006) — setup hook

After wake backend choice / confirm wake test, **optionally** offer I006 enrollment:
`hark wake-enroll` (or setup step) with beep-paced loop:
`[ready beep] → phrase → [captured beep] → … → [end beep]` (N=5–10).
Does not block Sherpa ship; link SETUP.md when I006 lands. Beeps via `audio.cues`.